LoveRance (ónyé amụrụ Rance Love Oliver II) bụ ónyé America rapper, onye na-emepụta ihe na DJ si San Francisco Bay Area
A maara ya nke ọma màkà egwu egwu ya nke afọ 2011 bụ "Up!" nke gosipụtara 50 Cent ma mepụta ya site na Iamsu!. "Up!" kụrụ nọmba 46 na US Billboard Hot 100 na nọmba abụọ na chaatị Rap.
E tinyere vidiyo egwu màkà egwu egwu LoveRance bụ "UP!" na akaụntụ Vevo ya na Jenụwarị 31, 2012. Vidio ahụ na-ewere ọnọdụ na Bay Area ma na-edekọ ọtụtụ n'ime vidiyo ahụ n'ime klọb abalị.
